---
title: "Evaluation_dashboard"
output: flexdashboard::flex_dashboard
runtime: shiny
---

```{r setup, include=FALSE}
  source("msum.R")
vstring = starwars%>%select_if(is.character)%>%names()
```

Input {.sidebar}
-----------------------------------------------------------------------

```{r}
selectInput("fby", "Filter By",choices = vstring, selected = "name")
textInput("fvalue", "Filter Value")
selectInput("grvalue", "Groupe By",choices = vstring,multiple = T)
```

Output
-----------------------------------------------------------------------

### Chart 

```{r}
renderTable(
  {
    starwars%>%msum(fby = input$fby,fvalue = input$fvalue,
                    grvalue = input$grvalue)
  }
)
```
